{"tid":740933,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大圍站部份月台突沉降20毫米 港鐵即時叫停新世界上蓋工程","createTime":"2018-07-13T09:14:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-14T10:26:18.000Z","uid":39464,"like":119,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":84,"replies":[{"pid":"fd14faecba722e17431f0a62f04b65091b0827f3","tid":740933,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T09:14:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180713/large/1531472815_3b82.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180713%2Flarge%2F1531472815_3b82.jpg&h=d06752b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n港鐵今日表示，東鐵綫大圍站2號月台第12卡車位置，在昨晚例行檢查時發現沉降至20毫米，據港鐵稱已要求新世界地產即時停止上蓋發展項目工程，並已邀請屋宇署及機電工程署視察，暫時並沒有影響行車安全。新世界發展表示承建商並因應港鐵公司的要求，即時暫停在東鐵綫相關鐵路保護區內的地基工程。<br />\n<br />\n新世界表示一直有委託結構工程師定期監察發展項目毗鄰的大圍站沉降情況，在昨日（7月12日）發展商與港鐵公司代表聯合檢查時，發現大圍站南行綫月台末端位置及附近出現輕微沉降，結構工程師已即日向屋宇署通報。新世界表示會繼續密切監察有關發展項目的情況，並與港鐵及相關政府部門保持緊密聯繫，以配合港鐵鐵路安全措施。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180713/58438280\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180713%2F58438280&d=qbA0rtXWdwE9mYCSP4H%2BOwdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=555b3db7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180713%2F58438280&h=f5d67a9b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180713/58438280</a>"},{"pid":"086281e2b441e9870ea9adfda3d31a143460f1ab","tid":740933,"uid":111153,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T09:15:16.000Z","msg":"會唔會冧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7625e7ddacc1ab1c7dfc7b52aafc43826ce309be","tid":740933,"uid":42767,"like":4,"dislike":15,"score":-11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T09:16:05.000Z","msg":"今獲唔係牙膏咁簡單, 坐坐下車都有機會出軌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{